The paper proposes a method for automatic neural architecture design, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of several sub-fields in computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL). Given that the paper focuses on image classification and language modeling tasks, it is most likely to be categorized under cs.LG and cs.CV, followed by cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.CL.
